CombinedLoss class

This class combines all the losses:
1. basic mse loss between predicted HR and GT HR frame (as in paper)
2. mocomp loss between predicted frame and reference frame (as in paper)
3. huber loss for the flows themselves (to keep them small? as in paper)
4. perceptual loss for vgg16 (our addition to this work)

I have also added variables alpha, beta, gamma and lam to control the
effect of these losses.

This assumes that you are using the eager training method rather than
the keras fit method.
